These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
House: craftsman, colonial, cape-cod, townhouse
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
2. the colonial house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
3. the craftsman house is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| House   | cape-cod | colonial | craftsman | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, lavender, green, ivory
1. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Color   | lilac | green | lavender | ivory |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, hip-hop, house, ambient
1. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Music-Genre   | house | jazz | hip-hop | ambient |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
